OL,3,CBBC One and ITV 1 News at Ten: the
OL,4,Clegacy of a bad decision in 1998
OL,6,GNext week marks the 25th anniversary
OL,7,Gof the end of the original run of what
OL,8,Gwas then called the ITN News at Ten.
OL,10,FThe controversy which surrounded the
OL,11,Fdecision is a reminder of another age.
OL,13,FSome ITV companies argued for the move
OL,14,Fas soon as the network was deregulated
OL,15,Fin 1993.
OL,17,FBut it took the ITC five years to
OL,18,Fallow what was initially a one-year
OL,19,Fexperiment.
