OL,3,CBBC One and ITV 1 News at Ten: the
OL,4,Clegacy of a bad decision in 1998
OL,6,FSo on 5th March 1999, the ITN Early
OL,7,FEvening News at 5.40pm and ITN News at
OL,8,FTen came to end. The following Monday
OL,9,Fthe ITV Evening News at 6.30pm and the
OL,10,FITV Nightly News at 11pm got underway.
OL,12,FBut, of course, we all know how it
OL,13,Fturned out. It wasn't pretty for ITV.
OL,15,FA shortened News at Ten returned three-
OL,16,Ftimes-a-week in early 2001.
