OL,3,CBBC One and ITV 1 News at Ten: the
OL,4,Clegacy of a bad decision in 1998
OL,6,FInitially its format copied the
OL,7,Fprogramme's glory days. The titles
OL,8,Faped those of 1988 and Trevor McDonald
OL,9,Fbriefly came out of retirement.
OL,11,FIt is all a sorry saga. The ITC, in
OL,12,Fretrospect, should not have allowed
OL,13,FNews at Ten to end in 1999.
OL,15,FBut we are where we are. Linear news
OL,16,Faudiences have fallen significantly
OL,17,Fsince then.
OL,19,FITV's commitment to the scheduling of
OL,20,FNews at Ten today seems lukewarm.
