OL,3,CBBC One and ITV 1 News at Ten: the
OL,4,Clegacy of a bad decision in 1998
OL,6,FIt is regularity pushed back for all
OL,7,Fsorts of reasons. In the coming week
OL,8,Fit is on late twice because of
OL,9,FCelebrity Big Brother. This scheduling
OL,10,Fwill probably continue all through
OL,11,FMarch.
OL,13,FTo be fair, later editions sometimes
OL,14,Frate well ` especially if they benefit
OL,15,Ffrom a big inheritance on the day of a
OL,16,Fbig story.
OL,18,FBut it is hard to build up a dedicated
OL,19,Faudience when the programme dances
OL,20,Faround the schedule.
