OL,3,CBBC One and ITV 1 News at Ten: the
OL,4,Clegacy of a bad decision in 1998
OL,6,FI still believe it is in nobody's
OL,7,Finterests for both principle channels
OL,8,Fto show their late news at the same
OL,9,Ftime.
OL,11,FITV should move its late news back to
OL,12,F10.30pm.
OL,14,FIf you believe in media plurality, you
OL,15,Fwill know that some news junkies might
OL,16,Factually want to watch both.
OL,18,FIt is a good thing to see two high
OL,19,Fquality programmes made by different
OL,20,Forganisations ` each with many
OL,21,Fstrengths.
