OL,3,CBBC One and ITV 1 News at Ten: the
OL,4,Clegacy of a bad decision in 1998
OL,6,FThose who want to, can see different
OL,7,Ftreatments of the same story and see
OL,8,Fdifferent sets of original and
OL,9,Fexclusive stories.
OL,11,FHowever until ITV is able to screen
OL,12,Fmore ads in peak time there is little
OL,13,Fcommercial incentive to move News at
OL,14,FTen back permanently.
OL,16,FWhen ITV runs a big programme through
OL,17,Fto 10.30pm, some advertising is
OL,18,Fdropped earlier in the evening.
OL,19,FOrdinarily there are no ads between
OL,20,Fthe start of News at Ten and 11pm.
