OL,3,CBBC One and ITV 1 News at Ten: the
OL,4,Clegacy of a bad decision in 1998
OL,6,FImagine if you could only look at one
OL,7,Fnews website or read one newspaper.
OL,8,FIt's unthinkable in a democracy. Yet
OL,9,Fthat is, in effect, the case when it
OL,10,Fcomes to two of the most important
OL,11,Fnews programmes in the country.
OL,13,FNow imagine being able to watch both
OL,14,FBBC One and ITV 1's main news each
OL,15,Fevening again regularly.
OL,17,FThis may seem a strange statement to
OL,18,Fmake coming from someone who cares
OL,19,Fabout journalism and public service
OL,20,Fbroadcasting but moving News at Ten to
OL,21,F10.30pm could actually be in the
OL,22,Fpositive public interest.
